headline: Agentic AI Poised to Handle 68% of Customer Service and Support Interactions by 2028
summary: Cisco (NASDAQ: CSCO) today announced the findings of its latest global research report, "The Race to an Agentic Future: How Agentic AI Will Transform Customer Experience," highlighting the potential of agentic AI to revolutionize the way technology vendors deliver services and support to customers.

headline: 3 S&P 500 Stocks Facing Headwinds
summary: While the S&P 500 (^GSPC) includes industry leaders, not every stock in the index is a winner. Some companies are past their prime, weighed down by poor execution, weak financials, or structural headwinds.
